items.title: Market ends lower in second week amid persistent FIIs selling; rupee hits new low
items.description: The India rupee touched fresh record low of 86.70 during the week and closed lower by 64 paise to end at 86.61 per dollar on January 17 against the January 10 closing of 85.97.
